No. 143,

Misc.,

October Term, 1953.

Shelton v. United States. Petitioner pro se. Solicitor General Sobeloff for the United States.

The motion to vacate the order of November 30, 1953, 346 U. S. 892, dismissing the petition for writ of certiorari is denied.

Mr. Justice Harlan took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
